name: Trash Poetry
description:
Trash Poetry is a song I wrote in September 2021. 

I wished to talk in this piece about the subtleties which surround us as a small stories which gives narrative thread for our lives in the everyday.

This a song I like to sing often in different ways, changing voice hues and rhythms

Lyrics, guitar, post arrangements and cover drawing.
Recorded at home studio the 18 from 2022's February
